{"tid":1657087,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"修例風波：保安閘遭質疑不安全 港鐵強調不會駁電","createTime":"2019-10-16T02:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T02:18:10.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69c4c9b5d203ce122fd0205649fe519a5e757c16","tid":1657087,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:15:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E9%96%98%E9%81%AD%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%A7%81%E9%9B%BB-004635807.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2596%2598%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A7%2581%25E9%259B%25BB-004635807.html&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVvlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=0ceef0e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E9%96%98%E9%81%AD%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%A7%81%E9%9B%BB-004635807.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XxZOYUUd96lFHLpTTfJZXw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDU2/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-10/5831fdd0-efae-11e9-9ffd-487b7b24654a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXxZOYUUd96lFHLpTTfJZXw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDU2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-10%2F5831fdd0-efae-11e9-9ffd-487b7b24654a&h=46683f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵加設的保安閘被質疑接駁電源後有安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵多個車站在修例風波中被破壞，港鐵發通告澄清坊間多項不實指控。當中有人指車站內部分標示為受破壞設施仍運作正常，質疑港鐵誇大受損程度。港鐵回應稱，部分設施包括八達通增值機、扶手電梯等表面上看似未受破壞，其實有零件受損，未能穩定運作，故在設施上貼上未能使用告示，待復修及相關測試完成後，將盡快恢復服務。<br />\n<br />\n至於最近於個別車站出入口加設保安閘，加強車站關閉後保安，但有指保安閘接駁電源後有安全問題。港鐵重申，有關設備不會接駁電源，車站會依據指示以人手拉開及收起。供應商已就安全閘設計及應用向公司提交安全報告，港鐵亦已將新增設備通報政府部門。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人質疑警方出現在已關閉車站，港鐵重申港鐵網絡治安是由鐵路警區負責，當有任何涉及治安的事件都會交由警方處理。若警方接獲情報，得知個別車站或有機會受到攻擊，或會因應情況派員前往車站執勤。<br />\n<br />\n另外，由於近期暴力破壞升級，港鐵指雖已靈活調配不同設備或零件作維修，惟部分與票務設施有關零件已耗盡，未能替換，現離全部零件運抵還需一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買電閘但人手做<br />\n中間食左幾多油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409d1478558913a7aa91a09bcb9f6cacef5824ca","tid":1657087,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2f7eb8ea647f1f2486e80d1e85459f83dcf09eea","tid":1657087,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"路障首選"},{"pid":"dc2610d7a98adcc9b02ec4817088e58a7b4651a9","tid":1657087,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:18:10.000Z","msg":"屌你大陸呀？"}]}